author: Sean Meagher | The Oregonian/OregonLive
title: Watch: Gary Crowton sees 'tons of energy' and 'progress' from Beavers
text: Gary Crowton , the former BYU head coach and offensive coordinator with LSU and Oregon who Oregon State head coach Gary Andersen says has a "tremendous football brain," met with the media following Wednesday's practice to talk about what brought him to Corvallis as an offensive consultant for the Beavers .
